program TestLexer;
{ Test harness for the OCaml lexer.
  Reads OCaml source from stdin, tokenizes it, and prints
  each token on a separate line in the format:
    KIND value
  where KIND is the token name and value is the literal. }

{ Include the lexer source }
{ Since p24p doesn't have an include mechanism, the lexer
  code is copied here. In the final interpreter, all modules
  will be in one file. }

